OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784060308
OL,3,CMore than 500-strong anti-GST protest
OL,4,Cahead of States debate
OL,6,FHundreds of islanders gathered in
OL,7,FGuernsey to protest the proposed
OL,8,Fintroduction of a Goods and Services
OL,9,FTax (GST), ahead of a States debate
OL,10,Fnext week.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, politicians will
OL,13,Fconsider a series of wide-ranging tax
OL,14,Freforms, including a 3% GST, which
OL,15,Fwould be brought in within 18 months.
OL,17,FToday's gathering was the latest in a
OL,18,Flong line of demonstrations against
OL,19,FGST proposals, with more than 500
OL,20,Fpeople in attendance at Market Square
OL,21,Fin St Peter Port.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
