OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784060308
OL,3,CMore than 500-strong anti-GST protest
OL,4,Cahead of States debate
OL,6,F33 people in Alderney held their own
OL,7,Fanti-GST protest at the same time.
OL,9,FThe Policy and Resources (P&R)
OL,10,FCommittee's proposed package aims to
OL,11,Fplug the island's financial black hole
OL,12,Fwhile supporting lower earners.
OL,14,FAs well as bringing in GST, it looks
OL,15,Fto reduce the basic level of personal
OL,16,Fincome tax to 15% for those who make
OL,17,Fup to #28,000 a year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784060308
OL,3,CMore than 500-strong anti-GST protest
OL,4,Cahead of States debate
OL,6,FSocial security contributions would
OL,7,Falso be adjusted, with a new allowance
OL,8,Fof #11,12 for employed and self-
OL,9,Femployed people, and an increase in
OL,10,Femployer contributions to 7.6% by 2029.
OL,12,FThe Committee says the changes would
OL,13,F"improve public finances by an
OL,14,Festimated #59 million a year".
OL,16,FHowever, some politicians, including
OL,17,FDeputy Rob Curgenven, believe P&R
OL,18,Fshould be considering a visitor levy
OL,19,For a so-called wealth tax, rather than
OL,20,Fintroducing GST.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784060308
OL,3,CMore than 500-strong anti-GST protest
OL,4,Cahead of States debate
OL,6,FDeputy Curgenven told ITV News:
OL,7,F"Firstly there's sorting out our
OL,8,Fexpenditure, getting our balance sheet
OL,9,Fand our financial statements right and
OL,10,Fseeing where we are and then we're
OL,11,Flooking at the revenue.
OL,13,FHe added: "We could also look to
OL,14,Ffreeze the overseas aid, which is 5.6
OL,15,Fmillion (pounds). And of course Deputy
OL,16,FCollins has definitely got lots of
OL,17,Famendments and proposals too."
OL,19,FDeputy Haley Camp also agrees that
OL,20,Fother options have been overlooked by
OL,21,FP&R.
OL,26,@wD@IpmwD@Ppn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
