OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784060308
OL,3,CMore than 500-strong anti-GST protest
OL,4,Cahead of States debate
OL,6,FDeputy Camp said: "This idea that
OL,7,Fwe've turned over every stone just
OL,8,Fdoesn't ring true to me.
OL,10,F"I've been in the States for 12
OL,11,Fmonths. I don't hear a lot about
OL,12,Fsavings, efficiencies, optimisation. I
OL,13,Fthink the package that's being
OL,14,Fpresented is one that feels very
OL,15,Floaded on one side in order to gain
OL,16,Fthe trust back but that other piece of
OL,17,Fwork needs to be done so it feels like
OL,18,Fa whole package that's completely
OL,19,Fthought out."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
